class="comment-content"><p>Sara, the only time I&#39;ve done that was my cinnamon buns. I&#39;m sure it would work, but I&#39;d be guessing at the timing of it.</p><p>I&#39;d put it in the fridge &#8212; wrapped tightly in plastic wrap with a little oil on it so it doesn&#39;t stick &#8212; after shaping it but before the second rise. Take it out the next day and leave it someplace warm until doubled in size. I really have no guess how long that will take, but certainly longer than if you don&#39;t refrigerate it.</p></div><div
